During Ramzan the mosque is very attractive with colorful bulbs.

featured_reviews.review_id:
"Jamia Masjid Usman bin Affan RZA"

Welcomes all of you with hands spread to all without any discrimination of caste and religion towards the oneness of the  Almighty Allah with the foundation of Modern and Islamic Education for both worlds.

Open for all communities to learn the true religion with the teachings of our beloved prophet Muhammed peace be upon him and the Holy Quran with the day-to-day lessons on selected topics.

First time in the history of the Jangaon district the masjid is open for Ladies with separate arrangements to offer Friday salaah on the masjid premises.

Selected top-notch speakers are being brought for the Friday sermon to deliver an authentic talk from the Holy Quran and Authentic Hadeeths with all references.

The atmosphere is soothing and a good ambiance is found in the air to get attached to Allah the creator.

Come and seek knowledge under the guidance of preachers (Aalims).

If any of the people have any clarification or misconception about Islam can connect with the responsible persons of the management.

JazakAllahu Khairan
